ABOUT
With over 120 acres in gorgeous Highlands County, Leisure Acres is a perfect winter or year-round home. When you're ready to make Florida living a lifestyle, Leisure Acres is where you'll want to settle down. We have land lease lots and Mobile Manufactured home sites available. Lots range in size from 50x75 to 50x100.
It is lined with 40 undeveloped acres, most of which is wooded area and wetlands, creating a Florida-natural setting with immediate access to the best businesses and services in Highlands County. Leisure Acres is an exciting community! There is a lot going on and we'd love for you to be a part of it!
.
OUR MISSION
​
​
To provide quality homes and a community in which homeowners are proud to live
To develop strong relationships with our residents in a climate of honesty and sincerity
To make sure that our customers receive the best housing value for their investment
​
OUR FAMILY
Leisure Acres community is family owned and operated. It was first acquired in 1978. Since then, it has grown and developed into a thriving community to which we are proud to be apart. Three generations and counting!
.
